const tintColor = '#2f95dc';

export default {
  tintColor,
  tabIconDefault: '#ccc',
  tabIconSelected: tintColor,
  tabBar: '#000000',
  errorBackground: 'red',
  errorText: '#fff',
  warningBackground: '#EAEB5E',
  warningText: '#666804',
  noticeBackground: tintColor,
  noticeText: '#fff',
  text: '#000000',
  content: '#ffffff',
  background: '#000000'
};
